Close UAT issues 2 + 3 + 5 from the 2026-06-18 widget-parity audit by collapsing the LegalWorkspace SmartTodo shim to Calendar's canonical Pattern D shape (no section title, no section toolbar) and rebuilding the widget's PaneHeader as the sole chrome â€” title "Smart To Do", single toolbar with `[SearchBox, +, Open, refresh]`. Result: one title, one toolbar, search lives in the toolbar.
