  <goal>
The SmartTodo workspace widget renders ONE title bar ("Smart To Do") and ONE toolbar containing `[SearchBox, +, Open, refresh]`. The LegalWorkspace shim becomes structural-only (no section title, no section toolbar) â€” mirrors `calendar.registration.ts` shape exactly. Search filters the rendered list locally (no OData round-trip needed for v1). Open button is selection-aware (disabled until a card is selected). The widget continues to mount cleanly in BOTH system-loaded and user-added workspace contexts.
  </goal>

