The 4 `<ui-tests>` blocks in this POML require a deployed environment (spaarkedev1 SpaarkeAi workspace). Per the durable user instruction, no branch deploy was attempted â€” these tests will be run after the main session pushes Wave D-1 (099+101) into master and the master-deploy re-pushes spaarkedev1.

### Carry-forward findings (for R4-100)

- R4-100's "Open-to-form launch protocol" will further modify `todo.registration.ts` â€” specifically the `handleOpenTodo` callback (currently still using the legacy `eventId=â€¦` data envelope at lines 75-86 of the rewritten shim) needs to swap to the `openTodo` discriminator. The pre-099 `data = `eventId=â€¦`` comment is preserved in the rewritten file as a hint for R4-100.
- R4-101's grouping sees ALL items in their respective buckets and the widget toolbar's `+` button (my Add) is wired to R4-101's grouped rendering correctly because both consume `filteredItems` (search-filtered) and group it.
